  - Combat-Action=Symbolism
By: St Thomas Aquinas
---
It can be shown from three sources that God is one. First from His
simplicity.  ... Secondly ... from the infinity of His perfection Thirdly ...
from the unity of the world. For all things that exist are seen to be ordered
to each other.
